title: Drafting the Most Exciting Things for Week 2
description:
This week, Sheil is joined by Lindsay Jones to draft the things they are most excited about for Week 2, including Lamar Jackson (7:00), Aaron Rodgers (17:00), and Saquon Barkley (21:00). Then, they team up to answer your mailbag questions from Week 1 (27:00).
Host: Sheil Kapadia
Guest: Lindsay Jones
Associate Producer: Mike Wargon
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal and Conor Nevins
